This extension adds your checklists to the report. To use this you need to add a variable in the report template for each checklist you want to include.

If your checklist is named "OWASP TOP 10" then the variable would be `${checklist-owasp-top-10}`

The variable name is always the lowercase name of your checklist with the spaces replaced with `-` and prepended with `checklist`.
